<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Sample responses:</p>
<ul>
      <li>A playground. Square meters, because it’s a large area so I would use a larger square unit.</li>
      <li>A tile. Square inches, because a square meter would be larger than the tile.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


