  <!-- Síntesis de la actividad -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="synthesis-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Select students to share responses for 3–5 things they saw around the classroom (or school).</li>
      <li>For each object or space that students present, ask if others also chose that object or space and if they chose the same square unit: 
        <q>¿Se podrían usar otras unidades cuadradas para medir esta área?</q>
      </li>
      <li>
        <q>¿Cómo decidieron cuál unidad cuadrada usar para medir cada área?</q>  (I thought about whether the area was a smaller area or a larger area. I chose small units for smaller areas and larger units for larger areas. I thought about how carefully I would want to measure the area.)
      </li>
    </ul>
  </paragraphs>


